Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez host HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/24.

Ebro talks about Beyonce and the Tiffany diamond, Rowdy Rebel addresses his Summer Jam mishap (1:13), Rosenberg feels terrible from traveling (16), and Laura Stylez does her patented Flashing Lights segments (38 & 1:08).
